00:18:18,913 --> 00:18:20,863
- Stirling, kembalilah!
- Ayo.

315
00:18:21,940 --> 00:18:23,748
- Stirling, kembali!
- Mary?

316
00:18:23,761 --> 00:18:25,501
- Stirling!
- Mary.

317
00:18:25,503 --> 00:18:26,614
Stirling, kembali!

318
00:18:26,620 --> 00:18:27,334
Mary!

319
00:18:27,390 --> 00:18:28,522
Stirling! Stirling!

320
00:18:28,729 --> 00:18:29,436
Stirling!

321
00:18:29,467 --> 00:18:31,477
Tidak, tidak, tunggu. Mary.

