00:26:35,645 --> 00:26:37,495
Waktunya penyempurnaan,

424
00:26:37,508 --> 00:26:39,731
ritual, upacara, misteri.

425
00:26:39,733 --> 00:26:40,982
Tidakkah kau penasaran?

426
00:26:46,472 --> 00:26:47,544
Shh...

